text: Neuwiller is a commune. It is found in the Haut-Rhin department of eastern France. It is on the border to Switzerland. ==Related pages== * Communes of the Haut-Rhin department ==References== *INSEE commune file ==Other websites== * Porte du Sundgau - Services de Neuwiller * Eurodistrict Basel Category:Communes in Haut-Rhin
